  <brief_title>A Comparison Of Local Anesthetic Agents And Steroid On Tracheal Tube Cuff</brief_title>
  <acronym>LA-STEROID</acronym>
  <official_title>A Comparison Between Local Anesthetics and Topical Cortikosteroids That is Applied to the Area of Cuff of Tracheal Intubation Tube in Pediatric Patients</official_title>
